To get TeX hyphenation dictionaries manually, run in this directory:

	tmp="$(mktemp -d)"
	trap 'rm -rf "$tmp"' EXIT
	wget -O "$tmp/hyphenation-utf8.zip" https://mirrors.ctan.org/language/hyphenation-utf8.zip
	unzip -j "$tmp/hyphenation-utf8.zip" \
	  'hyph-utf8/tex/patterns/txt/hyph-*.pat.txt' \
	  'hyph-utf8/tex/patterns/txt/hyph-*.hyp.txt' \
	  -d .

If you want to reduce resulting program size, compress dictionaries:

	gzip -f hyph-*.txt

The Taskfile get-dictionaries target performs these steps automatically.
